      • xOffset

        X-offset (pixels) from origin 0, 0.

      • yOffset

        public int yOffset
        Y-offset (pixels) from origin 0, 0.

      • opacity

        public int opacity
        Opacity value - meaningful only with multiple bitmaps of the same PrintType.
        • 0 = All pixels opaque, except pure white" instances
        • 1 (default) = All pixels opaque, including "pure white" instances

      • fillColor

        public int fillColor
        Background fill color.
        • 0 = All pixels off (white)
        • 1 = All pixels on, mono panel
        • RGB = Hex values for color (0xFFFFFF = white)
        • FillType for ZC Series Printers.

      • overprint

        public boolean overprint
        Applies to Uv PrintType only.
        • true = prints the Uv panel to a fresh panel of transfer film

      • preheat

        public int preheat
        Sets the amount of baseline energy used on the non-printed (white areas) of the card. Increasing the value from 0 will make the transition from non-printing (white) to printing (color or black) stronger.
        • ZMotif Series printers only.

      • graphicType

        public GraphicType graphicType
        Type of graphicData.

      • graphicData

        public ZebraCardImageI graphicData
        Bitmap image data.
